            </div>
            <div class="ml-5">
                <div class="details">
                    <h4>Detalles</h4>
                    <div class="profile">
                        <p><%= profileDetails.firstName %> <%= profileDetails.lastName %></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bank">
                        <!-- <h4>Bank Account Details:</h4> -->
                        <p><%= bankDetails.receiveBank.bankName %></p>
                        <p><%= bankDetails.receiveBank.accountNumber %></p>
                        <p><%= bankDetails.receiveBank.type %></p>
                    </div>
                    <hr />
                    <h4>Detalles de la agente</h4>
                    <div class="profile">
                        <p><%= agent.name %></p>
                        <p><%= agent.email %></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bank">
                        <p><%= agentBank.bankName %></p>
                        <p><%= agentBank.accountNumber %></p>
                        <!-- <p><%= agentBank.type %></p> -->
                    </div>

                    <hr />

                    <div class="transaction">
                        <div class="">
                            <p><span>Cantidad:</span><span class="text-right"> <%= transaction.fromAmount %>
                                    <%= transaction.fromCurrency %></span></p>
                            <p><span>Recibir:</span><span class="text-right"> <%= transaction.toAmount %>
                                    <%= transaction.toCurrency %></span></p>
                        </div>
                        <hr />
                    </div>
                    <p>Si tiene alguna pregunta, simplemente responda a este correo electr贸nico o p贸ngase en contacto
                        con nuestro equipo de soporte para obtener ayuda.
                    </p>
                    <p>Salud,
                        <br>The Moni Team</p>

                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <table class="email-footer" align="center" width="570" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"
                                role="presentation">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="content-cell txt-center">
                                        <p class="f-fallback sub align-center">&copy; 2020 Moni. All rights
                                            reserved.</p>
                                        <p class="f-fallback sub align-center">
                                            Moni
                                            <br>1234 Street Rd.
                                            <br>Suite 1234
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>